In this project 3 routers are connected.
To connect 3 routers the following configurations are done:
In Router 0:
#en
# config t
#int g 0/1
#ip address 192.168.10.1 255.255.255.0
#no shut
#exit
#ip dhcp pool ABC
#network 192.168.10.0 255.255.255
#default-router 192.168.10.1
#ip dhcp excluded-address 192.168.10.1
#ip dhcp pool DEF
#exit
#int g 0/0
#ip address 10.10.10.1 255.255.255.252
#no shut
#exit
# ip route 192.168.20.0 255.255.255.0 10.10.10.2 (router 1)
#ip route 192.168.30.0 255.255.255.0 10.10.10.2 (rouet 2)
#exit
#write memory

